<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionIRI> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo/0.1.1> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "DAIMO is an integration profile that connects DCAT-AP, MLDCAT-AP, ODRL, PROV-O, and the Dataspace Protocol (DSP, as operationalised by Eclipse EDC) to support publication, discovery, invocation, execution traceability, and contextualised evaluation of AI model assets exchanged in data spaces. The edc: namespace is used only for EDC-specific extensions (e.g., ParticipantContext) not yet standardised in DSP."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2026-04-22"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-04-22"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "DAIMO: an ontology for governed AI model assets in data spaces"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/preferredNamespacePrefix> "daimo" .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/preferredNamespaceUri> "https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#" .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "See daimo-ontology-design.md for the full design rationale."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionInfo> "0.1.1" .
